    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient must sign the informed consent form prior to the index-procedure.

          -  Patient with failed RYGB defined as patients with EWL &lt;50%.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient has a life expectancy of less than 2 year.

          -  Patient who is most likely expected not to be compliant with the proposed follow-up
             visits.
      </textblock>
